channel.title: 2012 Remake
channel.description: G'day everyone, just letting people know that me and a couple of friends have decided to code a 2012 server, pre eoc! A lot of progress has come to it already and i really think that this is going to work! Please give us your support if your interested about joining the beta by signing up at http://preeocscape.enjin.com/home. Screenshots coming soon! :)
